  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/315070/extras/c9217bd8a067744dc27d7ef2f11be298.avif?t=1666624349\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Blob From Space is a 2d sidescroller game with an interactive story. In the story mode we learn the origin of Blob joining the Defenders of the multiverse.<br>The game comes with challenging levels, but easy to learn.<br><br>Blob From Space powers:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Change into enemies.<br></li><li> Walljump like you have never experienced before!</li></ul><br>Mini games of the game will come in the future.<br>All mini games will come with new achievements!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/315070/extras/1c94b60d892e3f66777fc3bbf9b4a73c.avif?t=1666624349\" width=200 height=100 /></span>",
